&lt;p&gt;As a Research Scientist/Engineer focused on honesty within the Finetuning Alignment team, you&#39;ll spearhead the development of techniques to minimize hallucinations and enhance truthfulness in language models. Your work will focus on creating robust systems that are accurate and reflect their true levels of confidence across all domains, and that work to avoid being deceptive or misleading. Your work will be critical for ensuring our models maintain high standards of accuracy and honesty across diverse domains.&lt;/p&gt;
